title: xmrchaos
author: xmrchaos
content: Hello;I recently found a token I added years ago on my Metamask wallet, I don't really remember how I got this significant amount but I found it worth +$900.I want to exchange or swap this token or sell it. The token is known as "smARTOFGIVING" (AOG).I have tried some swapping services and platforms but they require high fees, I couldn't do the swap because I don't have the required ETH to acquire the action.I have also found that I can do the swap ifÂ  I bridge the coins from ETH mainnet to BNB network. But unfortunately, I couldn't find the token in question to bridge it to BNB.If there is any suggestion on how to can I exchange it, or if anybody is interested in buying them you can leave me a comment or send me a DM.Thanks in advance.
